    "description": "Sac's Bar Holdings Inc. engages in the retail sale of bags, fashion goods, and related accessories in Japan. It also offers ladies' bags, luggage, small items, and other products. In addition, the company is involved in retail of purses, wallets, and miscellaneous goods; planning, manufacturing, and selling of canvas bags and accessories; and sells men's and travel bags. It operates approximately 600 stores. The company operates shops under the SAC'S BAR, GRAN SAC'S, LAPAX, DOUX SAC'S, and NAUGHTIAM brand names. The company was formerly known as Tokyo Derica Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Sac's Bar Holdings Inc. in October 2014. The company was incorporated in 1974 and is based in Tokyo, Japan."
